# Lightning record -from 

1. base component
2. Switches between view and edit modes automatically when the user begins editing a field in a view form
    means -> 
3. Uses the object's default record layout
4. Loads all fields in the object's compact or full layout, or only the fields you specify


Important  _attributes :
 1. object-api-name : this attributes is always required   
 2. record-id  : it is required only when the user is editing or viewing the record 
 
 
 
